Gene Rayburn https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gene_Rayburn 0 Gene Rayburn (December 22, 1917 – November 29, 1999) was an American radio and television personality. He is best known as the host of various editions of the popular American television game show Match Game for over two decades.
